'''希爾思寵物營養公司'''（{{lang-en|Hill's Pet Nutrition, Inc.}}），為[[高露洁-棕榄|高露洁-棕榄]]旗下的子公司，是美國[[犬粮|犬粮]]及[[猫粮|猫粮]]生產商，其產品以希爾思（Hill's）品牌推出市場。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Early_Picture_of_Hill_Packing_Company.jpg|thumb]]
希爾思由伯頓·希爾（Burton Hill）於1907年春天建立，本稱希爾提煉工程（Hill Rendering Works）<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/140426/burton_hill_death_has_hill_company/ |title = Estherville Daily News, 18 September 1962 page 1 |access-date = 2020-11-02 |archive-date = 2019-02-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190217084910/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/140426/burton_hill_death_has_hill_company/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite web |url = http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=pv&GRid=67624323&PIpi=66653241 |title = Builders of Topeka 1934 |access-date = 2020-11-02 |archive-date = 2017-04-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170424175500/https://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=pv&GRid=67624323&PIpi=66653241 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，主要為[[肖尼縣_(堪薩斯州)|肖尼縣]]處理死去及殘缺的動物，其副產品用於製造農場飼料。
至1930年，公司易名為希爾包裝公司（Hill Packing Company）。除了新增的碾磨部門之外，公司亦有生產供人食用的[[馬肉|馬肉]]，每星期屠宰及處理500匹馬<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/138072/hill_packing_rep_visits_500_head_per/ |title = The Belleville Telescope, 1 September 1932 page 1 |access-date = 2020-11-02 |archive-date = 2019-02-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190217031759/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/138072/hill_packing_rep_visits_500_head_per/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，出口到[[挪威|挪威]]、[[瑞典|瑞典]]、[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]及[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]<ref name="#1"/><ref name=ad>{{cite web|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/138075/trade_horses/|publisher=[[Belleville_Telescope|Belleville Telescope]]|title=Trade horses for sale (classified ad)|date=September 29, 1932|page=12|access-date=2020-11-02|archive-date=2019-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217030410/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/138075/trade_horses/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = https://archive.org/stream/serviceregul2811930unit/serviceregul2811930unit_djvu.txt | title=SERVICE AND REGULATORY ANNOUNCEMENTS, Sep 19030}}</ref>。

1968年，希爾包裝公司被{{le|里維亞納食品|Riviana Foods}}收購<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/riviana-foods-inc-history/ |title = Riniana Foods Inc. History |access-date = 2020-11-02 |archive-date = 2020-10-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201015160450/http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/riviana-foods-inc-history/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。1976年-{}-里維亞納食品與[[高露洁-棕榄|高露洁-棕榄]]合併<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/138106/colgatepalmolive_to_merge_with_riviana/ |title = The Des Moines Register, 13 February 1976 page 25 |access-date = 2020-11-02 |archive-date = 2017-04-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170406110712/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/138106/colgatepalmolive_to_merge_with_riviana/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

